main_body:
The following paragraph shall be added to Article 5 of Directive 74/561/EEC:
"3. With regard to Greece, the dates in paragraphs 1 and 2 shall be replaced as follows:    - in paragraph 1, "1 January 1978" shall be replaced by "1 January 1984";
- in paragraph 2, "31 December 1974", "1 January 1978" and "1 January 1980" shall be replaced by "31 December 1980", "1 January 1984" and "1 January 1986" respectively."
